Netherlands’ De Jager Says Euro Crisis Talks Will Be Tough

-- B y   F r e d   P a l s
-- 
2011-10-21T12:12:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-21/netherlands-de-jager-says-euro-crisis-talks-will-be-tough.html
Dutch Finance Minister  Jan Kees de
Jager  said a meeting today of euro area finance chiefs “will be
tough and the situation is serious.”  “We really need to step up efforts, make extra reforms,
extra cuts and strict agreements on budgets,” he told reporters
before the meeting.  To contact the reporter on this story:
